<p>是同类，嘎嘎嘎嘎嘎嘎嘎嘎嘎嘎嘎（开始尖啸）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacketjiong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6151941); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6151941&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600471973" alt="JacKeTJioNG" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6151941)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacketjiong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6151941); return false;">JacKeTJioNG</a></span></p>
<p>柿饼，好吃，恰恰恰恰恰恰啊 ――<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4423816&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600471973" alt="Dr_Naxurt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4423816)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;">Dr_Naxurt</a></span></p>
<p>关于用柿子替代企鹅作为奇术材料以减少基金会开支的提案已经提交 ――<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/e-u" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6176669); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6176669&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600471973" alt="E_U" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6176669)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/e-u" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6176669); return false;">E_U</a></span></p>
<p>柿饼柿饼我是馅饼！wwwwww ――<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/auroriaaaaa" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5474061); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5474061&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600471973" alt="Auroriaaaaa" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5474061)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/auroriaaaaa" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5474061); return false;">Auroriaaaaa</a></span></p>
<p>管他什么柿饼，真男人就该吃企鹅！ ――<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6114202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600471973" alt="Frozen starry sky" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6114202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;">Frozen starry sky</a></span></p>
<p>已展开“企鹅能否进食柿子”的相关调查 ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lanperouge" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6332347); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6332347&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600471973" alt="lanperouge" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6332347)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lanperouge" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6332347); return false;">lanperouge</a></span></p>
<p>草，原本随口一说，结果真连到邮筒主页了!——<span class="error-inline"><em>Dr diurnal night</em> 不匹配任何一个现有的用户名</span></p>
<p>企鹅，好。 ――<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doppelganger-lynn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6670691); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6670691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600471973" alt="Doppelganger_Lynn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6670691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doppelganger-lynn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6670691); return false;">Doppelganger_Lynn</a></span></p>
